The areas herein declared for housing purposes shall be disposed of in accordance with the provisions of Republic Act No. 274 in relation to the provisions of Commonwealth Act No. 141, as amended otherwise known as the Public Land Act.

The unoccupied portions of the area covered by the proposed proclamation which are found to be suitable for housing purposes shall be disposed of in favor of the qualified beneficiaries as identified by the Local Inter-Agency Committee (LIAC) chaired by the Housing and Urban Development Coordinating Council (HUDCC);

The portions of the area herein reserved for housing purposes and declared open for disposition, that are being used or earmarked for public or quasi-public purposes shall be excluded from such disposition.

A Local Inter-Agency Committee (LIAC) is hereby created composed of the Housing and Urban Development Coordinating Council (HUDCC) as Chair, the Local Government Unit of Los Baños as Vice-Chairman and the Department of Environment and Natural Resources (DENR), Presidential Commission on Urban Poor (PCUP), and the representative of the respective homeowners association as members. The LIAC shall prepare the implementing rules and regulations (IRR) of this proclamation.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 17TH day of FEB, in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Four.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

